reviewText: well for a start it will not play on American t.v sets had to watch it on my computer and when I bought it it did not say that it would not play on our t.vs

My daughter has all of the Monkisee videos.  This one has many different animals in it. It doesn't have quite as many different songs as Around the House. And it isn't as interactive as Action Words. But it is still fun and educational. My daughter knows almost all of the farm animals and what sound they make. My favorite animal sou d she makes is Cockadoodledoo. Your child will enjoy this video (and this series) as well.
